									-The Payer Claim Control Number as it would be returned on the 835 2100 CLP07.  This number must apply to the entire claim. Please use an identifier.type of DCN.  
								   - If available, the Claim Identifier for Transmission Intermediaries as sent to the payer on the 837 2300 Ref*D9. Please use an identifier.type of D9
									</xs:documentation>
